ERRORS/MISCELLANEOUS
--------------------
The -irix patch fixes an unfortunate nameclash that is caused by a define
in sys/socket.h on irix.

The -trio patch add support for linking with the trio string library for
snprintf/vsnprintf support instead of using the included snprintf.c

